a nine-year drought Brought torrent in May you have choose what to call me but be give a new name always the strong one you carry on in faith broken mother , break father it be your example that make grace fully tangible look at your mistake show me what risk to take work hard to make end meet no matter what , please know you do well by me forever humble and first to forgive treat the other as family never forget where you have be you show us what it mean to wholly live adorn with quiet strength you prove that meek do n't have to mean weak Learned to show love to all , no matter title or rank while not your own , you have help raise me and for the thing you have show me I could hardly offer sufficient thanks even as the sickness linger in your blood you have carry on in hope and love and even though trouble surround all the while you have continue to greet all with a heavenly smile we watch your body fade but until the end , your spirit show bright something that cancer could never take away we lay hand on and pray Oh G-d , how steadfast you stay how I wish I have possess such faith now we feel the weight of your absence and it have raise some doubt and question but in memorial we will press on because , in the end , it be all you ever want for your son that we might realize our dream live life beautifully to truly glean all we can from our youth let the rest of our life stand as proof there be a point to all of this to learn to love as you _____________ name mother artist be as an Ocean album how we both wondrously Perish